{"tid":253272,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭俊弘幸福肥 自爆未帶何雁詩見家長","createTime":"2017-05-22T09:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T16:21:41.000Z","uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f271891d05298e4fb71164975a2cd96fcd61ec7","tid":253272,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"鄭俊弘（Fred）跟車婉婉為《媽媽好聲音》歌唱比賽擔任評判，Fred獲逾百粉絲來撐場，新手媽媽車婉婉產後首復工。同何雁詩認戀半個月，鄭俊弘竟然幸福到發福，他早前返加拿大探望媽咪就未有帶何雁詩一齊：「他們想見我多一點」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n離上次公開露面相距近1個月，Fred超快現幸福肥。脹爆的Fred謂這期間忙於錄第3張專輯外，早前更返加國探望家人。問到是否趁機紓緩壓力？說：「都是吧！每年都會返去一次，特別是舅母煮好多餸給我吃，好開心見到他們」。Fred謂女友何雁詩未有同行，家人亦沒有過問感情事。問家人會否想見阿詩？他說：「他們想見我多一點。」對於女友早前面對網友負評不高興，Fred表示女友心情還好。問女友有否服藥治療情緒？他說：「這些要問回她啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/4/2061818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F4%2F2061818&d=OeNbSnhVY7UVR%2FdNhh%2F7B0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4bf56b14\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/4/2061818</a>"},{"pid":"5d908d2896f6204498f110774b5d4bf72d89c353","tid":253272,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"牙fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f744440ea25dfea5be5eaeff9b726a3909397b7","tid":253272,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"c263dc35d3c060df6884efe802586b5b0d612178","tid":253272,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:37:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>wfc</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40ba19b9f787c904d1e41a9902723399ffba406","tid":253272,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>wfc</blockquote><br />\n(Show blocked user - david)"},{"pid":"540e2079b7728043429710f0f6d5c244bfacac55","tid":253272,"uid":53947,"l